item.title: 2021 IEEE MTTS Student Design Competition
item.description: Figure 1: 13.56 MHz Converter Figure 2: MTTS award 2021 Student Design Competition on High-efficiency power amplifier for 13.56 MHz The 2021 IEEE International Microwave Symposium (IMS) was held in June 7-10 at Atlanta, Georgia. IMS is one of the largest events for the RF and Microwave Industry attended by hundreds of academic institutions and companies across the world. During this conference, student attendees were able to participate in a Student Design Competition.
